==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pentadactyle
<hw>Pen`ta*dac"tyle</hw> }</mhw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>pentada`ktylos</grk> with
five fingers or toes. See <er>Penta-</er>, and <er>Dactyl</er>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Having five digits to the hand or
foot.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having five appendages resembling fingers or
toes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pentadactyloid</ent>⟦br⟧
